    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s absolutely pristine inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new car feel. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and looks brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
