    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen that presents exactly as it did on the showroom floor. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings to be found. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, preserving all rubber seals and trim in factory-fresh condition. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and remains smoke-free. The premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the carpets have been protected by original equipment manufacturer floor mats since day one. Every technological feature, from the navigation system to the ambient lighting, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is detailed and spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. We have the complete service history, all original keys, and the original window sticker available. This is a rare find for a buyer who demands perfection and a vehicle that needs absolutely nothing but a new home.",
      "price": 44500.0,
