    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is in total showroom condition. It\u2019s like stepping back in time\u2014not a single scratch, the interior still has that fresh smell, and it drives as smooth as silk. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it truly looks and feels brand new. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Swing by and take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
