    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a showroom-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six mated to a factory 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen is mechanically superlative: the 'Big Three' have been addressed with documented rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan components, and a proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The powertrain retains its factory 8,000 RPM redline integrity, breathing through individual throttle bodies with precise mapping. The chassis is tightened with refreshed bushings and a limited-slip differential that remains silent and tight. Zero fluid seepage, a pristine undercarriage, and an interior free of typical soft-touch wear. This is a definitive, investment-grade example of the ultimate driving machine, maintained to a standard that exceeds factory specifications.",
